layout.text:
Tikettak is a must-have car accessory. With Tikettak you can avoid parking fines and say goodbye to that sticky mess left on your car windows and windscreen.
Tikettak can also be used around the home & office. Use Tikettak to post notices on walls, fridges, PCs and on the outside doors for postal delivery instructions!
